The evidence with the title 'Hating the hate crimes bill - OnFaith ' says Oct 13, 2009  ... The Matthew Shepard and James Byrd Jr. Hate Crimes Prevention Act seeks to expand federal hate - crime statutes to include protections for homosexuals.  ... Opponents claim the legislation would ( 1 ) make it a crime to denounce homosexuality from the pulpit , and (2) give legal protection to pedophiles. 
